{"tid":1103730,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"返工比隻老鮑魚屌","createTime":"2019-04-12T15:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T15:22:50.000Z","uid":70065,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d76bae6ce2eac8cfd745666d3f2fb51596e50d58","tid":1103730,"uid":70065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"話說我返寫字樓工 有個新入職既大陸老鮑魚入左黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢日日朝頭早就拎d蒸包返到位先用蒸煮器整熱<br />\n搞到我個位附近都勁撚多水煮氣 唔講仲以為佢食大麻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到左今日 近排開始熱 我見到d蒸氣係我附近 就細細聲講左句 屌你隻臭鮑魚 食包就返屋企啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢聽到 就去左搵我上司 話我鬧佢仆街 仲周圍問人點解我叫佢做鮑魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我轉頭就比我上司叫左入房 叫我同事之間好好相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0f96afeab83bb0c0b15742a52175a843a15032","tid":1103730,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，明明就係你面皮成尺厚咁問我可唔可以請你食件包<br />\n咁大家又唔熟我又餓咪話唔得<br />\n點知你咁小氣仲要小學雞改人花名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858e308d2b486a15e81975509c95f3193056afbe","tid":1103730,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"巴打做中資？"},{"pid":"0f1f7b2dbe15ca6ead232dd42cb0aecec14aa9c0","tid":1103730,"uid":70065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"858e308d2b486a15e81975509c95f3193056afbe","tid":1103730,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"巴打做中資？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得揀都唔想做"},{"pid":"6f2166c99f986da92db8a306a6b7b56b44b2dabc","tid":1103730,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"作文?<br />\n如果唔係既, 你都無理由無啦啦講粗口啦, 唔出warning算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4d28b2d4da57232e5db8a0954713d77f282d39","tid":1103730,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"等佢無啦啦大煙大乂聲問佢係咪食緊大麻"},{"pid":"f259a4b1e246d6460450c6d0fe8a3d9e63a46302","tid":1103730,"uid":206565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"樓主on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係人地影響到你，自己大條道理屌柒佢都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個女人咁做埋啲小動作"},{"pid":"ba80d2cfe1d9e0ff41c53a3494c0655cb9c1e3fc","tid":1103730,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f1f7b2dbe15ca6ead232dd42cb0aecec14aa9c0","tid":1103730,"uid":70065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"858e308d2b486a15e81975509c95f3193056afbe","tid":1103730,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"巴打做中資？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得揀都唔想做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"喺中資行你同大陸婆嘈冇著數<br />\n大陸人同聲同氣。"}]}